1. Distribution
Total Supply: 250,000,000 SRC
Circulating Supply: Dynamic (based on burn stages)
Owner Wallet: 0xb73997C19722aCe8FA3b4178301D1828Bc89E9E9
Tax Wallet: 0xF9A8Bb84ef445b9499bB0a4E088A321F54B621F9
2. Tax Structure
Buy Tax: 5%
Sell Tax: 10%
All tax fees are sent to the official tax wallet for liquidity management and ecosystem operations.

3. Burn Mechanism
SRC includes two owner‑initiated burn phases:

Burn Stage One
Burns 10% of total supply
Executed via:
burnStageOne()

One‑time irreversible function
Burn Stage Two
Burns 5% of total supply
Executed via:
burnStageTwo()

One‑time irreversible function
4. Smart Contract
License: MIT
Standard: BEP‑20 (ERC‑20 compliant)
Verified On‑Chain: June 12, 2025
Contract includes Tax, Burn Stages, Automated Supply Reduction, and Event Logging.
Full source code is available in the main repository.

5. Project Overview
SilkRoadCoin (SRC) is the official digital asset powering the SmartMarket ecosystem of Achaemion Holding FZE.

The token is designed for secure payments, marketplace utilities, supply‑controlled economics, and integration across the Achaemion financial architecture.

Official website: https://src.achaemion.com

Email: ceo@src.achaemion.com

End of Tokenomics
